{"body": "With carlosantioniodasilva's suggestion, there is no need for an `:unknown` type column.  Also, Rails column types attempts to mimic the most common column types across databases, and there is no such thing as an \"unknown\" column type in databases.\r\n\r\n:thumbsdown: on the unknown column type idea\r\n:thumbsup: on the raise on invalid column type idea", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/9453994", "created_at": "2012-10-15T17:36:07Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7954#issuecomment-9453994", "updated_at": "2012-10-15T17:36:42Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7954, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mhuggins/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mhuggins/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mhuggins/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mhuggins", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mhuggins/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/mhuggins", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mhuggins/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/781f66c42983ae7ee3123bbd620d8568?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F8cc10a343f7cacddbbc5488786f3f22b.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mhuggins/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mhuggins/received_events", "gravatar_id": "781f66c42983ae7ee3123bbd620d8568", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mhuggins/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "mhuggins", "type": "User", "id": 169093, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mhuggins/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237f759bd3543c15100b02f"}, "id": 9453994, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/7954"}
